For example, upgrades between 1.14.x -&gt; 1.15.x or 1.15.x -&gt; 1.16.x are allowed, however 1.14.x -&gt; 1.16.x is not allowed. The node pool minor version must be within two minor versions of the control plane version. The node pool version cannot be greater than the control plane version.             title="Optional">
